                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200918-296-defend2714 t18200918-296-deflabel1699"></join>d to me from the Marine Society, and has been two years and a half in my service; I keep a haberdasher's shop. On the 19th of July she ran away; I saw her in the street and had her brought back; I talked to her about robbing me of other things, and said I would forgive her. In the evening I missed these things Pilgrim brought them to my house.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
