            . My husband is a rag merchant. The prisoner came to my house between seven and eight o'clock in the morning, and left a bundle containing these articles; she said she had left Mrs. Gardener, and I endeavoured to persuade her to return - she said she would not. Soon after Mrs. Gardener came; she saw her and ran away.</p>
